document_data.mainbody:
'''''Beneath the Lonely Tower''''' was an adventure module for the D&D Game Day in March 2010, for the 4th edition of ''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]''.

{{Quote|''In the frontier village of Beorunna's Well, all is not well. Villagers have disappeared without a trace, and the locals fear to walk alone at night. Now the villagers hear distant cries of terror in the night, echoing from an abandoned fortress outside the village. A group of brave heroes must step forward to explore the Lonely Tower and end the threat to Beorunna's Well.''


''“Beneath the Lonely Tower” is a 6th-level adventure with six pre-generated characters included, all using options from the new Player’s Handbook 3.''}}
